ðŸ¤– Key Ethical Themes in the "Elements of AI" Course

AI's Societal Impact
The course emphasizes the profound effects AI can have on various aspects of society, including employment, privacy, and decision-making.

Bias and Fairness
It highlights the importance of recognizing and mitigating biases in AI systems to ensure fairness and equity.

Transparency and Explainability
The course discusses the need for AI systems to be transparent and their decisions explainable to users.

Accountability
It underscores the necessity for clear accountability in AI development and deployment to address potential harms.

Privacy and Data Protection
The course touches on the importance of safeguarding personal data and respecting user privacy in AI applications.
